    - Hello?? Who are you?? What are you doing here??
    - My name is Evelyn. Nice to meet you Ilo!
    - Ohh... So you are looking for a person named Milo?
    - No. Unfortunately i haven't seen anyone.
    - You want me to help you escape the mine?
    - Okay! First grab the latern in front of you to have some light during your
      path.
    - I have heard of a worker saying you have to pull a lever in order to move a
      hatch.
    - But you have to know the code first. It is said to be inside a locked chest.
      Hope you can find the key.
    - After solving this you will  be able to climb the ladder in order to escape.
    - Your time is limited Ilo! See you on the other side.
    - I have to go... Byee...
